ntact-item"><a href="https://github.com/angkasa27" aria-label="Link: https://github.com/angkasa27" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/angkasa27</a></li><li class="contact-item"><a href="https://asaa.dev" aria-label="Link: https://asaa.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://asaa.dev</a></li></ul></div></header><div class="layout-body"><section class="section" data-section="summary"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Summary</h2><div class="rich-text"><p>Software Engineer with 5+ years of experience specializing in frontend development for enterprise web applications. Skilled in building responsive, high-quality interfaces with modern frameworks, improving performance, and creating maintainable component-based systems. Comfortable working beyond the frontend when needed, including API integration, system design, and deployment, to deliver reliable end-to-end products.</p></div></section><div><section class="section" data-section="workExperience"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Work Experience</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title">Nusantara Commerce</h3><em class="meta italic">Lead Frontend Engineer</em><span class="meta">Jakarta, Indonesia</span></div><div class="item-header-side"><div class="item-date">Mar 2022 - Current</div></div></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Led the migration of the customer storefront from legacy React pages to Next.js App Router, improving Core Web Vitals and reducing average page load time by 38%.</li><li>Partnered with product and design teams to launch a reusable component library used by 6 squads, cutting feature delivery time by 25%.</li><li>Mentored 4 engineers through architecture reviews, testing standards, and rollout plans for high-traffic releases.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="skills"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Skills</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><h3 class="item-title">Frontend Engineering</h3><span class="meta">React, Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Design Systems, Vitest, Playwright</span></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="projects"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Projects</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><h3 class="item-title"><a href="https://portfolio.example.dev/projects/seller-analytics-dashboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Seller Analytics Dashboard</a></h3><span class="item-date">Jan 2024 - Oct 2024</span></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Built a role-based analytics dashboard for marketplace sellers with interactive charts, exports, and saved filters.</li><li>Implemented data fetching and cache strategies that reduced dashboard query time from 5.2s to 1.9s on high-volume accounts.</li><li>Delivered an accessible UI and keyboard-first navigation, passing internal accessibility QA for core flows.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="education"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Education</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title">Institut Teknologi Bandung</h3><em class="meta italic">B.S. in Informatics</em><span class="meta">Bandung, Indonesia</span><span class="meta">GPA: 3.78 / 4.00</span></div><span class="item-date">Aug 2015 - May 2019</span></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Focused on software engineering, human-computer interaction, and distributed systems.</li><li>Capstone project: designed a web-based scheduling platform used by 3 departments during pilot adoption.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="publications"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Publications</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><p class="rich-text" style="margin:0"><em><a href="https://medium.com/@dimasangkasa/frontend-performance-ecommerce" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Practical Frontend Performance for Indonesian E-Commerce</a></em> — Tech in Asia Community (Sep 2024).</p><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Wrote a practical guide on bundle optimization, image strategy, and rendering patterns based on production incidents and measurable outcomes.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="certifications"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Certifications</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title"><a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/12345678-90ab-cdef-1234-567890abcdef" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AWS Certified Developer - Associate</a></h3><em class="meta italic">Amazon Web Services</em><span class="meta">Credential ID: AWS-DEV-2024-5521</span></div><span class="item-date">Jul 2024</span></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="awards"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Awards</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title">Product Impact Award</h3><em class="meta italic">Nusantara Commerce</em></div><span class="item-date">Dec 2024</span></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Recognized for leading checkout performance improvements that increased conversion by 6.4% during the year-end campaign period.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="languages"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Languages</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item item-row"><h3 class="item-title">English</h3><em class="meta italic">Professional working proficiency</em></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="references"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">References</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><h3 class="item-title">Pertiwi Putri</h3><em class="meta italic">Engineering Director, Nusantara Commerce</em><span class="meta">pertiwi.putri@nusantaracommerce.co.id · +62 812-4455-6677</span></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="organizationVolunteering"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Organizations &amp; Volunteering</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title">Indonesia React Community</h3><em class="meta italic">Volunteer Mentor</em><span class="meta">Jakarta, Indonesia</span></div><span class="item-date">Feb 2021 - Current</span></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Mentor junior developers through monthly frontend clinics covering React fundamentals, testing, and portfolio reviews.</li><li>Co-organized 8 meetups with hands-on workshops attended by more than 400 participants.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></article>"`;

