class="section" data-section="skills"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Skills</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><h3 class="item-title">Frontend Engineering</h3><div class="meta">React, Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Design Systems, Vitest, Playwright</div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="projects"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Projects</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><h3 class="item-title"><a href="https://portfolio.example.dev/projects/seller-analytics-dashboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Seller Analytics Dashboard</a></h3><div class="item-date">Jan 2024 - Oct 2024</div></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Built a role-based analytics dashboard for marketplace sellers with interactive charts, exports, and saved filters.</li><li>Implemented data fetching and cache strategies that reduced dashboard query time from 5.2s to 1.9s on high-volume accounts.</li><li>Delivered an accessible UI and keyboard-first navigation, passing internal accessibility QA for core flows.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="section" data-section="education"><h2 class="section-heading" data-testid="resume-preview-section-heading">Education</h2><div class="item-list"><div class="item"><div class="item-header"><div class="item-header-main"><h3 class="item-title">B.S. in Informatics</h3><div class="meta">Institut Teknologi Bandung · Bandung, Indonesia</div></div><div class="item-header-side"><div class="item-date">Aug 2015 - May 2019</div><div class="meta">GPA: 3.78 / 4.00</div></div></div><div class="rich-text"><ul><li>Focused on software engineering, human-computer interaction, and distributed systems.</li><li>Capstone project: designed a web-based scheduling platform used by 3 departments during pilot adoption.</li></ul></div></div></div></section></div><div><section class="se